  m_text: 'LMB (hold + release) - drag

    RMB - switch blocked state

    ctrl
    + lmb - add node

    ctrl + rmb - delete node

    alt + lmb - add link (from-to)

    alt
    + rmb - delete link

    mouse scroll - change link cost

    ? + LMB - start

    ?
    + RMB - finish'
